    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300023053_7_484-502",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "484-502",
      "markText": "窗内漆黑一片，柔柔娇喘无力传至窗外。",
      "totalCount": 544,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300023053&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=484&rangeEnd=502",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/94932900813ab6f81g0132f2?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=484&rangeEnd=502"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300023053_13_37028-37121",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "37028-37121",
      "markText": "诺顿房间里的灯亮着，床上没有人。他转身冲向阁楼，到了楼梯顶，一个撤步，如勒马悬崖。三脚架倒了，望远镜横在地板上。上方几英尺处，孩子挂在暗影丛林里，就在横梁下面，他从那里将自己射向了太空。",
      "totalCount": 442,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300023053&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=37028&rangeEnd=37121",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/94932900813ab6f81g0132f2?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=37028&rangeEnd=37121"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300023053_7_20500-20543",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "20500-20543",
      "markText": "于是，当格林栎夫先生跑到她身边时，她的样子就像是趴在那畜生的耳畔向它低语她最后的发现。",
      "totalCount": 418,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300023053&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=20500&rangeEnd=20543",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/94932900813ab6f81g0132f2?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=20500&rangeEnd=20543"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300023053_7_7467-7567",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "7467-7567",
      "markText": "他讨厌乡下，讨厌他过的日子；他讨厌与母亲还有傻哥哥一起生活，讨厌听到关于该死的奶牛、该死的雇工、该死的破机器的话。可是尽管这么说，他却从未有过打算离开的举动。嘴上说着巴黎和罗马，却连亚特兰大都没去过。",
      "totalCount": 357,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300023053&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=7467&rangeEnd=7567",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/94932900813ab6f81g0132f2?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=7467&rangeEnd=7567"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300023053_9_24362-24391",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "24362-24391",
      "markText": "但圣灵，以寒冰而非以火为纹饰的圣灵，不管不顾地持续降下来。",
      "totalCount": 289,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300023053&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=24362&rangeEnd=24391",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/94932900813ab6f81g0132f2?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=24362&rangeEnd=24391"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300023053_9_6960-7017",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "6960-7017",
      "markText": "“我没有想象力。我没有才华。我不能创造。我只有对这些的渴望。你为什么不把那渴望也杀死？女人，你为何剪掉我的羽翼？”",
      "totalCount": 266,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300023053&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=6960&rangeEnd=7017",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/94932900813ab6f81g0132f2?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=6960&rangeEnd=7017"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300023053_6_850-879",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "850-879",
      "markText": "“遇听障人士，就大喊，遇视障人士，就把人物画得大而惊人”。",
      "totalCount": 221,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300023053&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=850&rangeEnd=879",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/94932900813ab6f81g0132f2?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=850&rangeEnd=879"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300023053_8_18637-18698",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "18637-18698",
      "markText": "他绝望地环顾四周，希望有人能够救他，但四周空无一人，只有一只巨大的黄色怪物坐在旁边，像他一样动也不动，只是大口大口吃着土。",
      "totalCount": 198,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300023053&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=18637&rangeEnd=18698",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/94932900813ab6f81g0132f2?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=18637&rangeEnd=18698"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300023053_16_19331-19366",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "19331-19366",
      "markText": "他就在那儿——那个自称俄巴底亚·以利户的人——倚着树干，哭得像个婴儿。",
      "totalCount": 195,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300023053&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=19331&rangeEnd=19366",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/94932900813ab6f81g0132f2?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=19331&rangeEnd=19366"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300023053_6_610-660",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "610-660",
      "markText": "1950年被诊断患有红斑狼疮，与母亲在安达卢西亚农场度过余生，酷爱养孔雀、雉等禽类。1964年去世。",
      "totalCount": 187,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300023053&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=610&rangeEnd=660",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/94932900813ab6f81g0132f2?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=610&rangeEnd=660"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300023053_9_3843-3862",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "3843-3862",
      "markText": "但她发现他们读的书越多，会干的事越少。",
      "totalCount": 187,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300023053&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=3843&rangeEnd=3862",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/94932900813ab6f81g0132f2?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=3843&rangeEnd=3862"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300023053_11_14498-14539",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "14498-14539",
      "markText": "黑暗的狂潮似乎又将他卷回到她身边，一刻又一刻，延迟着，不让他进入懊悔与悲伤的世界。",
      "totalCount": 187,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300023053&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=14498&rangeEnd=14539",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/94932900813ab6f81g0132f2?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=14498&rangeEnd=14539"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300023053_7_14402-14499",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "14402-14499",
      "markText": "斯科菲尔德将黄油递给她，说道：“唉，妈妈呀，那头牛也没干什么，不过是给你的牛群混进点劣等血统，你就要杀死一头老牛，你不感到惭愧吗？我宣布，”他说，“有你这么个妈妈，我能出落得这么好真是个奇迹！”",
      "totalCount": 180,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300023053&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=14402&rangeEnd=14499",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/94932900813ab6f81g0132f2?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=14402&rangeEnd=14499"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300023053_13_3343-3423",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "3343-3423",
      "markText": "“你不知道没有她，我也孤独吗？”谢播德说，“你以为我一点都不想她吗？我想，但我没有坐在那儿垂头丧气。我在忙着帮助别人。你什么时候见我干坐着，只考虑自己的难处？”",
      "totalCount": 180,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300023053&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=3343&rangeEnd=3423",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/94932900813ab6f81g0132f2?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=3343&rangeEnd=3423"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300023053_16_10793-10877",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "10793-10877",
      "markText": "画师又看了他一会儿，似乎不能完全确定。“你的气色不如以前啊，”他说，“肯定是蹲过大牢了。” “结婚了。”帕克说。",
      "totalCount": 176,
